      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🛡️ InvoiceGuard — Automated Invoice Fraud Detection & Approval Pipeline\n**Owner:** Finance Automation / Platform Engineering\n\nEnd-to-end pipeline that ingests inbound invoices, extracts structured data with AI, cross-checks them against InvoiceGuard's duplicate & anomaly detection API, scores fraud risk, routes for human approval when needed, posts approved bills to the accounting system and keeps a full audit trail. Includes a scheduled digest and a dedicated error-handling branch.\n\n_Portfolio sample — endpoints/credentials are illustrative placeholders._",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 880,
        "color": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8cf92756-775f-44b4-ab7c-0aa6614ca6fb",
      "name": "Note 2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -720,
        -260
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 1. Intake & Normalization\nWebhook receives the invoice (from email parser, upload UI or vendor portal), downloads the attachment if provided and normalizes the payload into a common schema.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 620,
        "color": 6
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e1fc5532-a133-4a6e-aee2-045486d58a0f",
      "name": "Note 3",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        780,
        -260
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 2. AI Extraction & Validation\nGPT-4o reads the invoice document/image and returns structured fields. The result is reconciled with the submitted metadata and validated before anything touches the database.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 620,
        "color": 6
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "61d32e2a-780a-4f06-a5fc-7004058cb8bc",
      "name": "Note 4",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1980,
        -260
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 3. Duplicate & Anomaly Detection\nMirrors InvoiceGuard's audit engine: vendor-name similarity + amount + date-window duplicate matching, and per-vendor z-score statistical outlier detection.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 640,
        "color": 6
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4c1ce2c0-6c75-41e8-9c05-1e9113590a0e",
