      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 4. Fraud Risk Scoring & Routing\nCombines every signal (duplicate score, anomaly score, round-amount, weekend issue-date, missing PO, new vendor) into a single 0–100 risk score and routes the invoice accordingly.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 640,
        "color": 6
